metadata.name: Primo
metadata.description:
Borneo, 1984
© Time Traveler AI


"The history is art, the photographer is only a witness. I will take you to where you’ve never been."

Time Traveler AI is a visual artist whose absorbing cinematic photography transports you to the alternate world that both existed and never did. A pioneer in Post-Photography since 2022. 

“Primo” is created exclusively for the AI Surrealism show in NY by Exquisite Workers and Superchief Gallery NFT, featuring 100 AI artists, on June 2-8, 2023.
